---
export const prerender = true;
import Shop from '@/layouts/Shop.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '@/components/astro/Breadcrumb.astro';
import BlogHero from '@/components/astro/BlogHero.astro';
import { tenant } from '@/config/tenant';

const publishDate = '2026-03-27';
const title = 'LOOP Nicotine Pouches: The Flavour-First Brand';
const description = 'Explore LOOP nicotine pouches — Swedish-made with Instant Rush technology for faster nicotine delivery. 32 products, bold flavours, and eco-conscious design.';
---

<Shop
  title={`${title} | ${tenant.name}`}
  description={description}
  ogType="article"
>
  <article class="bg-background text-foreground">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <Breadcrumb items={[
        { label: 'Blog', href: '/blog' },
        { label: 'LOOP Guide' },
      ]} />

      <BlogHero
        category="Brand Spotlight"
        title={title}
        description={description}
        date="March 27, 2026"
        readTime="8 min read"
      />

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground [&_h2]:text-foreground [&_h2]:text-2xl [&_h2]:font-bold [&_h2]:mt-10 [&_h2]:mb-4 [&_h3]:text-foreground [&_h3]:text-xl [&_h3]:font-semibold [&_h3]:mt-8 [&_h3]:mb-3 [&_strong]:text-foreground [&_a]:text-primary [&_a]:underline [&_a:hover]:text-foreground">

        <h2>What Makes LOOP Different?</h2>
        <p>
          In a market dominated by Swedish Match and BAT, <strong>LOOP</strong> carved out its own identity
          by refusing to play it safe. Made by Another Snus Factory (ASF) in Sweden and launched in 2019,
          LOOP's signature innovation is their <strong>Instant Rush technology — a pouch design that releases nicotine and flavour faster than traditional pouches</strong>. Where most brands take
          a few minutes to kick in, LOOP delivers a noticeable rush almost immediately. For a competitive comparison, see our <a href="/blog/zyn-vs-velo-2026">ZYN vs VELO guide</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          With 32 products in the <a href="/brands/loop">LOOP catalogue</a>,
          the brand also stands out for its adventurous flavour range. While <a href="/blog/zyn-nicotine-pouches-complete-guide">ZYN</a> and <a href="/blog/velo-nicotine-pouches-complete-guide">VELO</a> stick to variations of
          mint and berry, LOOP pushes into territory like jalapeño lime and habanero mint. If you find mainstream
          pouches a bit predictable, <strong>LOOP is the antidote for flavour explorers</strong>.
        </p>

        <h2>LOOP Formats: Mini and Slim</h2>
        <p>
          LOOP offers both <strong>mini</strong> and <strong>slim</strong> formats:
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Mini pouches</strong> are smaller and ultra-discreet, ideal for situations where you want
          zero visibility — meetings, commutes, or social settings. They deliver a gentler experience with
          less moisture and a shorter flavour window.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Slim pouches</strong> are the brand's flagship format. Longer and thinner than regular
          pouches, they sit comfortably under the lip and release more flavour over a longer session.
          The Instant Rush effect is most pronounced in the slim range.
        </p>

        <h2>LOOP Strength Range</h2>
        <p>
          LOOP covers the full spectrum from <strong>nicotine-free (0 mg) to extra strong (15.6 mg)</strong>:
        </p>
        <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse [&_th]:text-left [&_th]:p-2 [&_th]:border-b [&_th]:border-border [&_th]:text-foreground [&_td]:p-2 [&_td]:border-b [&_td]:border-border/50">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Strength</th>
              <th>Nicotine</th>
              <th>Best For</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Nicotine-free</td>
              <td>0 mg</td>
              <td>Flavour without nicotine, tapering down</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><a href="/products/strength/regular">Normal</a></td>
              <td>4–6 mg</td>
              <td>Everyday use, casual pouch users</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><a href="/products/strength/strong">Strong</a></td>
              <td>7–10 mg</td>
              <td>Regular users, former smokers</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><a href="/products/strength/extra-strong">Extra Strong</a></td>
              <td>12–15.6 mg</td>
              <td>Experienced users, high tolerance</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p>
          The nicotine-free option is worth noting — LOOP is one of the few brands that lets you enjoy
          the full pouch ritual without any nicotine, making it useful for people <a href="/blog/best-nicotine-pouches-for-quitting-smoking">reducing their intake gradually</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>LOOP's Signature Flavours</h2>
        <p>
          LOOP's flavour range is where the brand truly shines. While they offer excellent
          <a href="/products/flavor/mint">mint</a> and <a href="/products/flavor/berry">berry</a>
          options, the standout creations are the ones you won't find anywhere else. For mint comparisons across brands, read our <a href="/blog/top-10-mint-flavours">top 10 mint pouches article</a>:
        </p>
        <h3>Bold and Adventurous</h3>
        <p>
          Jalapeño Lime, Habanero Mint, and Salty Ludicris push the boundaries of what a nicotine
          pouch can taste like. These aren't gimmicks — they're carefully balanced flavour profiles
          that have built a loyal following among users who want something genuinely different.
        </p>
        <h3>Classic Done Well</h3>
        <p>
          For those who prefer familiar territory, LOOP's mint varieties are excellent — fresh,
          clean, and long-lasting thanks to the Instant Rush technology. The
          <a href="/products/flavor/citrus">citrus</a> and <a href="/products/flavor/berry">berry</a>
          options are equally refined, with natural-tasting fruit notes rather than artificial sweetness.
        </p>
        <h3>Coffee and Licorice</h3>
        <p>
          LOOP's <a href="/products/flavor/coffee">coffee</a> variants deliver rich, roasted flavour
          that pairs perfectly with a morning routine. The licorice options lean Swedish — authentic and
          slightly salty rather than candy-sweet.
        </p>

        <h2>The Instant Rush Experience</h2>
        <p>
          LOOP's proprietary Instant Rush technology deserves its own section because it genuinely
          changes how the pouch feels. <strong>Traditional pouches typically need 2–5 minutes before you notice the nicotine, while LOOP brings that down to under a minute for most users.</strong> This makes LOOP popular among <a href="/blog/best-nicotine-pouches-all-day-use">all-day users</a> seeking rapid onset.
        </p>
        <p>
          The trade-off is that the initial intensity is sharper — which some users love and others
          find surprising the first time. If you're used to a slow, gradual build-up, your first LOOP
          experience will feel notably different. Most users find the faster onset becomes preferable
          once they're accustomed to it.
        </p>

        <h2>Eco-Conscious Packaging</h2>
        <p>
          LOOP positions itself as the environmentally conscious choice. Their cans use recycled
          materials and the brand communicates sustainability as a core value rather than an afterthought.
          For users who factor environmental impact into their purchasing decisions, LOOP offers a way
          to enjoy nicotine pouches with a lighter ecological footprint.
        </p>

        <h2>Who Is LOOP Best For?</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Flavour explorers</strong> — If you've been using the same mint pouch for months
          and want to try something genuinely new, check our <a href="/blog/nicotine-pouch-flavour-guide">flavour guide</a> comparing LOOP against other adventurous brands.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Fast onset fans</strong> — If you find traditional pouches too slow to kick in,
          the Instant Rush technology delivers quicker satisfaction. Compare with <a href="/blog/how-long-do-nicotine-pouches-last">duration and onset across brands</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Brand switchers</strong> — If you're exploring beyond <a href="/blog/zyn-nicotine-pouches-complete-guide">ZYN</a>
          or <a href="/blog/velo-nicotine-pouches-complete-guide">VELO</a>, LOOP is the natural next step — Swedish quality with
          more personality. For a detailed comparison, see <a href="/blog/loop-vs-skruf">LOOP vs Skruf</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Eco-conscious users</strong> — If sustainability matters to you, LOOP walks the talk
          with recycled packaging and transparent environmental commitments. See our guide to <a href="/blog/nicotine-pouch-subscription-guide">sustainable pouch purchasing</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>LOOP vs Other Brands</h2>
        <p>
          Compared to <a href="/blog/zyn-nicotine-pouches-complete-guide">ZYN</a>, LOOP is bolder in both flavour and onset speed.
          ZYN is the reliable daily driver; LOOP is the one you reach for when you want something
          more exciting. See our full <a href="/blog/best-nicotine-pouches-2026">best nicotine pouches ranking</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Compared to <a href="/blog/velo-nicotine-pouches-complete-guide">VELO</a>, LOOP trades BAT's global polish for ASF's
          indie creativity. VELO has wider availability; LOOP has wilder flavours.
        </p>
        <p>
          Compared to other flavour-focused brands,
          LOOP's Instant Rush technology gives it a functional edge beyond just taste. For more brand comparisons, see our <a href="/blog/loop-vs-skruf">LOOP vs Skruf</a> article, or explore <a href="/blog/best-citrus-nicotine-pouches">citrus</a> and <a href="/blog/best-coffee-nicotine-pouches">coffee flavour guides</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Further Reading</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/blog/best-nicotine-pouches-2026">Best nicotine pouches 2026</a> — LOOP's overall ranking and comparison</li>
          <li><a href="/blog/loop-vs-skruf">LOOP vs Skruf</a> — head-to-head comparison of two Swedish innovators</li>
          <li><a href="/blog/nicotine-pouch-flavour-guide">Nicotine pouch flavour guide</a> — explore LOOP's adventurous flavours</li>
          <li><a href="/blog/top-10-mint-flavours">Top 10 mint nicotine pouches</a> — LOOP's mint lineup ranked</li>
          <li><a href="/blog/how-to-use-nicotine-pouches">How to use nicotine pouches</a> — guide to Instant Rush technology</li>
          <li><a href="/blog/best-citrus-nicotine-pouches">Best citrus nicotine pouches</a> — LOOP citrus vs competitors</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Cross-links -->
      <nav class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-border">
        <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Browse by Flavour</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <a href="/products/flavor/mint" class="rounded-full bg-muted px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-primary/10 transition">Mint</a>
              <a href="/products/flavor/berry" class="rounded-full bg-muted px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-primary/10 transition">Berry</a>
              <a href="/products/flavor/citrus" class="rounded-full bg-muted px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-primary/10 transition">Citrus</a>
              <a href="/products/flavor/coffee" class="rounded-full bg-muted px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-primary/10 transition">Coffee</a>
              <a href="/products/flavor/fruit" class="rounded-full bg-muted px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-primary/10 transition">Fruit</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Browse by Strength</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <a href="/products/strength/mild" class="rounded-full bg-muted px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-primary/10 transition">Mild</a>
              <a href="/products/strength/regular" class="rounded-full bg-muted px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-primary/10 transition">Regular</a>
              <a href="/products/strength/strong" class="rounded-full bg-muted px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-primary/10 transition">Strong</a>
              <a href="/products/strength/extra-strong" class="rounded-full bg-muted px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-primary/10 transition">Extra Strong</a>
              <a href="/products/strength/super-strong" class="rounded-full bg-muted px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-primary/10 transition">Super Strong</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 text-center">
          <a href="/brands/loop" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:text-foreground transition text-sm font-medium">
            Shop All LOOP Products &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Article",
        "headline": title,
        "datePublished": publishDate,
        "dateModified": publishDate,
        "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "SnusFriends Editorial" },
        "publisher": {
          "@type": "Organization",
          "name": tenant.name,
          "logo": { "@type": "ImageObject", "url": `https://${tenant.domain}/og-image.jpg` }
        },
        "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": `https://${tenant.domain}/blog/loop-nicotine-pouches-complete-guide` },
        "description": description
      })} />
    </div>
  </article>
</Shop>
